Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我买了你喜欢的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放在老地方 那个隐藏柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢那种东西的又不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来继续杀戮 继续死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.21,Logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,200)}曙光社字幕组\NSGS Fansub

Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:18.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Strict control of reason and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:23.16,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Cut myself and scream for their insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:27.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:32.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:49.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:53.67,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:58.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:02.44,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna make you bleed just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So make me your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With only poison in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.69,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in a battle I have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm gonna make you bleed like me
