Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:55.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪止不住 一直流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:23:04.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恨 恨这不公的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:12.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这座迷宫 想逃 却没有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:16.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追求自由的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:25.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倒立着 俯看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:34.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已经不是昨天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:40.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 夜空洒遍了星辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:49.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界竟如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:56.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光载满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:24:04.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是这般精彩
